  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After a terrorist-engineered virus crippled the world, humanity adapted the only way it could — on wheels. Now, survivors roll into battle in high-powered wheelchairs, armed to the teeth and ready to reclaim what’s left.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customize your rig, perfect your aim in the gun range, and prepare for fast-paced, tactical wheelchair warfare against players and bots across diverse maps and intense game modes.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Game Modes:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Team Deathmatch</strong> – Roll out with your squad and dominate the opposition.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Free For All</strong> – Everyone’s your enemy. Be the last one rolling.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Gun Game</strong> – Earn new weapons with every kill — no breaks, no mercy.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Last Man Standing</strong> – One life. One shot at glory.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Last Team Standing</strong> – Team up, no respawns. Win or get wiped out.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join our community, share your feedback, and help shape the future of <i>Wheels of Duty</i> </p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After a terrorist-engineered virus crippled the world, humanity adapted the only way it could — on wheels. Now, survivors roll into battle in high-powered wheelchairs, armed to the teeth and ready to reclaim what’s left.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customize your rig, perfect your aim in the gun range, and prepare for fast-paced, tactical wheelchair warfare against players and bots across diverse maps and intense game modes.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Game Modes:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Team Deathmatch</strong> – Roll out with your squad and dominate the opposition.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Free For All</strong> – Everyone’s your enemy. Be the last one rolling.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Gun Game</strong> – Earn new weapons with every kill — no breaks, no mercy.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Last Man Standing</strong> – One life. One shot at glory.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Last Team Standing</strong> – Team up, no respawns. Win or get wiped out.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join our community, share your feedback, and help shape the future of <i>Wheels of Duty</i> </p>",
